{
  "texts": [
    "These token-level rewards are then used to train policy models through algorithms such as PPO.",
    "However, the quality of these automatically generated rewards remains a concern.",
    "AI-generated annotations and credit assignment models are prone to errors, raising questions about the reliability of the rewards and, consequently, the overall quality of the trained policy models.",
    "In this paper, we investigate the integration of auto-labeled token-level rewards into preference optimization.",
    "We introduce T-REG, a novel tokenlevel preference optimization algorithm that leverages both sequence-level and token-level rewards."
  ]
}